    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamental deciduous tree species native to Japan, Korea, China, and Taiwan. In Japan its durability and easy working properties have led to its popularity as a building timber and as a wood for carved objects.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
